          "page": "37",
          "license": ""
        },
        "description": {
          "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The avulzor creates a skeleton out of a pile of bones or a the corpse of a Large or smaller creature within 10 feet of it. The skeleton is under the control of the avulzor, obeying the avulzor's mental commands, and uses the statistics of a <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-2.github.io/bestiary.html#blankhash,flsttype:undead=1,fbsr:skeleton,flstchallenge%20rating:min=&amp;0~max=&amp;1\">CR 1 or lower skeleton</a> of your choice. The avulzor can control up to three skeletons at one time. If the avulzor creates a skeleton while it already has three under its control, the oldest skeleton crumbles to dust.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
