        "description": {
          "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The avulzor wears a kilt made out of the bones of the many humanoids it has slain. The kilt increases the avulzor's Armor Class by 3. If lost, the avulzor can create a new bone kilt with ample bones and 1 hour of work.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>The avulzor can use its Animate Bones as a bonus action if it targets the bone kilt. Doing so creates 1 <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-2.github.io/bestiary.html#blankhash,flsttype:undead=1,fbsr:skeleton,flstchallenge%20rating:min=&amp;0~max=&amp;2\">skeleton of CR 2 or lower</a>, but the avulzor subsequently reduces its Armor Class by 3.</p></div>",
